    <notes>
      <change from="6.3.12" to="6.3.13">
        <items name="REGRESSION FIXES">
          <item><para>The multiline SMTP error fix in release 6.3.12
caused fetchmail to lose message codes 400..599 and treat all of these
as temporary error. This would cause messages to be left on the server
even if softbounce was turned off.</para></item>
        </items>

